"     Authors",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"UTD.htm?8/48/8967/contributors\">",
"     Karin Leder, MBBS, FRACP, PhD, MPH, DTMH",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"UTD.htm?8/48/8967/contributors\">",
"     Peter F Weller, MD, FACP",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"   </div>",
